# Emprata.ai Environment Variables

Copy this file to `.env` and fill in your actual values.

```env
# Google AI API
VITE_GOOGLE_API_KEY=your_google_api_key_here

# Kirvano Payment Integration
VITE_KIRVANO_CHECKOUT_URL=https://kirvano.com/checkout/your_code_here

# Firebase Configuration
VITE_FIREBASE_API_KEY=your_firebase_api_key
VITE_FIREBASE_AUTH_DOMAIN=your_project.firebaseapp.com
VITE_FIREBASE_PROJECT_ID=your_project_id
VITE_FIREBASE_STORAGE_BUCKET=your_project.appspot.com
VITE_FIREBASE_MESSAGING_SENDER_ID=your_sender_id
VITE_FIREBASE_APP_ID=your_app_id

# Admin Configuration
# IMPORTANT: Set this to your email to enable admin features
# Example: VITE_ADMIN_EMAIL=admin@emprata.ai
VITE_ADMIN_EMAIL=your_email@example.com
```

## Admin Setup

To enable admin features:
1. Add your email to `VITE_ADMIN_EMAIL` in `.env`
2. Restart the dev server
3. Login with that email
4. You'll see a shield icon in the top-left corner
5. Click it to access the Admin Control Panel

## Admin Features

- **Credit Management:** Add or remove credits (positive/negative values)
- **Plan Switching:** Test FREE/STARTER/PRO features
- **History Reset:** Clear editor state
